snippet.title: Gigantic - Alpha Gameplay PAX Prime 2014
snippet.description:
Developed by Seattle-based Motiga, Gigantic is a PC team action game with massive guardians and brave heroes.

Learn more at: http://www.gogigantic.com
Like: https://www.facebook.com/GoGigantic
Follow: https://twitter.com/GoGigantic
Watch: http://www.twitch.tv/gogigantic
